original_script = "IF wstMerchantDoor == 0 | GOTO | EGG_ENTER
IF wstMerchantDoor == 1 | GOTO | EGG_RECLAIM
IF wstMerchantDoor == 2 | GOTO | EGG_EMPTY

EGG_ENTER
DIALOG | P_NAME | Hmm... An egg shaped hole in the wall.
WAIT   | 0.5
IF @Influence Ovum@ >= 1 | GOTO | EGG_CHOICE

EGG_CHOICE
CHOICE | Use an Influence Ovum?
REPLY  | EGG_USE | Yes.
REPLY  | EGG_NAY | No.

EGG_USE
MOVETO | o_cts_hoopz | o_cinema0 | MOVE_NORMAL
WAIT   | 0
LOOK   | o_cts_hoopz | NORTH
WAIT   | 0.25
USEAT  | NORTH
SET    | o_wst_eggSwitch01 | filled
SOUND  | sn_mg_puzzlelock_open1
NOTIFY | Used an Influence Ovum!
ITEM   | Influence Ovum | -1
EVENT  | o_wst_eggSwitch01 | 0
WAIT   | 0.5
LOOK   | o_cts_hoopz | WEST
WAIT   | 2
SET    | o_wst_eggSwitch01 | used
QUEST  | wstMerchantDoor = 1

EGG_NAY
EXIT   |

EGG_RECLAIM
MOVETO | o_cts_hoopz | o_cinema0 | MOVE_NORMAL
WAIT   | 0
LOOK   | o_cts_hoopz | NORTH
WAIT   | 0.25
DIALOG | P_NAME | This egg is all drained out. I guess I might as well reclaim it.
USEAT  | NORTH
SET    | o_wst_eggSwitch01 | default
NOTIFY | Got an Empty Influence Ovum!
ITEM   | Empty Influence Ovum | +1
QUEST  | wstMerchantDoor = 2

EGG_EMPTY
DIALOG | P_NAME | There is no more use for this..."
